lead_paragraph: RAILROADS.--On Tuesday the electors of Rochester decide whether that city shall subscribe for $300,000 stock of the Genesee Valley Railroad: The success of the road is believed to be a matter of much importance to the interests of the city, and there is little doubt that the subscription will be voted.
